A7:   TopSpaceMetr(M)=TopStruct (#the carrier of M,Family_open_set(M)#)
      by PCOMPS_1:def 6;
      assume
      y in the carrier of TopSpaceMetr(M);
      then reconsider y as Point of M by A7;
      F1.y = dist(y,x) by A5
        .= F2.y by A6;
