A3: x1 in P and
A4: (dist(p1)).x1 = lower_bound((dist(p1)).:P) by A1,A2,Th21,Th22;
A5: TopSpaceMetr(M)=TopStruct (#the carrier of M,Family_open_set(M)#) by
